# `@proxed/logger`

Shared `pino` logger instance.

## Entry points

- `packages/logger/src/index.ts` exports `logger`

## Conventions

- Prefer `logger` over `console.*` in server code and background jobs.
- Log structured objects (context fields) rather than string interpolation.

